---
---

<section id="faqs" class="section section-tinted" aria-labelledby="faqs-heading">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">FAQs</div>
      <h2 id="faqs-heading" class="section-h2">Common questions before we build.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-wrap reveal">

      <div class="faq-filter-wrap" role="group" aria-label="Filter questions by topic">
        <button class="faq-filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
        <button class="faq-filter-btn" data-filter="general">Getting Started</button>
        <button class="faq-filter-btn" data-filter="website">Website &amp; SEO</button>
        <button class="faq-filter-btn" data-filter="care">Domain, Email &amp; Care</button>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list" id="faq-list">

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Do you only work with local businesses?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>ReadyStack Digital focuses on local businesses across Australia, including service providers, consultants, trades, recruitment businesses, clinics, restaurants and other businesses that need a professional online presence.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Do I need WordPress?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Not always. Most local businesses only need a fast, professional website with contact forms, SEO setup, secure hosting, domain connection and monthly care. We only recommend WordPress if your business specifically needs full website editing or plugin-heavy features.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="website">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Is SEO included?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Every website includes basic SEO setup, including page titles, meta descriptions, sitemap, heading structure, image alt text and Google Search Console setup.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="care">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Can you manage my domain and hosting?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We can help register or connect your domain, configure DNS, connect hosting, manage SSL and keep the technical setup monitored through monthly care.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="care">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Is business email included?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Business email is optional. We can help set up professional email such as info@yourdomain.com as an add-on, including support for required records such as MX, SPF, DKIM and DMARC.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="website">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Will my website be secure?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We include secure website foundations such as HTTPS, SSL checks, secure hosting setup, DNS checks and form testing. Where suitable, we use lightweight static websites to reduce unnecessary plugin and admin-login risks.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="care">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>What does monthly care include?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Monthly care includes hosting management, domain and DNS checks, SSL monitoring, contact form testing, basic SEO monitoring, Search Console checks and small updates depending on your plan.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="care">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Can you upload blog posts?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Blog support can be added. You can send us blog content, and we can upload, format and apply basic SEO settings.</p></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" data-cat="website">
          <button type="button" class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
            <span>Do you offer unlimited edits?</span>
            <svg class="faq-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>No. Monthly care includes small updates only. Larger design changes, new pages, copywriting, SEO campaigns or custom features are quoted separately.</p></div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
